lead_paragraph: Hull City's interim boss Mike Phelan has once again urged the club's hierarchy to get cracking on signing a few reinforcements with the end of the transfer window fast approaching.

headline.print_headline: Phelan Urges Hull Owners to Strengthen Squad
headline.main: Phelan Urges Hull Owners to Strengthen Squad
